OL,3,CWhy the number of MPs in Wales is
OL,4,Cbeing cut from 40 to 32
OL,6,FThere are new parliamentary
OL,7,Fconstituency boundaries for almost
OL,8,Fevery part of Wales at the 2024
OL,9,FGeneral Election.
OL,11,FOnly Ynys Mon is exempt from the
OL,12,Fchanges, with several Welsh seats
OL,13,Fhaving now vanished as the number of
OL,14,FMPs from Wales drops from 40 to 32.
OL,16,FThe new seat boundaries take effect
OL,17,Ffrom when voters head to the polls for
OL,18,Fthe General Election on 4 July.
