OL,3,CWhy the number of MPs in Wales is
OL,4,Cbeing cut from 40 to 32
OL,6,FFor that election in 2026, the
OL,7,Fconstituency boundaries will be based
OL,8,Fon the new parliamentary boundaries
OL,9,Fbut with a difference - they will be
OL,10,Fjoined together in pairs, to make 16
OL,11,F"super-constituencies" which will each
OL,12,Freturn six members.
